# Phase 2C – Azure CLI File Navigation & nano Mastery
---

---
## Section 1 - Objective
---

### Purpose

Develop operational mastery of Azure Cloud Shell file navigation and text editing using Bash and the nano editor.

### Desired Outcome

+ Ability to navigate the Linux file system using Bash CLI
+ Ability to create, edit, and manage files using nano
+ Understanding of GNU Readline behavior and keyboard interpretation
+ Awareness of browser limitations affecting CLI behavior
+ Ability to troubleshoot and adapt to Cloud Shell input constraints

### End of Section 1
