## Section 4 - Microsoft-Style Technical Table
---

### Table Markdown

| Field | Parent Command | Syntax | Interchangeable Terms | Explanation | Use Case | Analogy |
|------|------|------|------|------|------|------|
| pwd | bash | `pwd` | print working directory | Displays current directory | Confirm working location | GPS check |
| ls | bash | `ls -la` | list files | Lists directory contents | Inspect files | Looking inside a room |
| nano | bash | `nano file.txt` | text editor | Opens terminal editor | Edit files | Writing in notebook |
| Ctrl+O | nano | save | write file | Saves file | Persist data | Saving document |
| Ctrl+X | nano | exit | close editor | Exits nano | Finish editing | Closing notebook |
| Ctrl+W | nano | search | find | Searches text | Locate data | Ctrl+F |
| F6 | nano/browser | search alt | fallback search | Browser-safe search | Cloud Shell search | Backup tool |
| PgDn | terminal | page down | scroll | Moves view down | Navigate file | Scroll page |
| PgUp | terminal | page up | scroll | Moves view up | Navigate file | Scroll up |
| Alt+B | readline | backward word | word jump | Moves cursor backward | Faster navigation | Jump words |
| Alt+F | readline | forward word | word jump | Moves cursor forward | Faster navigation | Jump words |

### End of Section 4
